    public abstract class FormElement<T extends FormElement,V extends FormElementViewHolder>
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Base-class for form elements to be used with SimpleFormDialog

    Each form element holds a resultKey that is used to receive element specific results in SimpleFormDialog.onResult(int) Created by eltos on 20.02.17.
